ividual assessments that you can run immediately without any configuration steps.","pos":[2866,3059]},{"content":"In addition, when you create a new job, predefined jobs are available as templates.","pos":[3060,3143]},{"content":"A job that is created from a template can also be run without modification or additional configuration steps.","pos":[3144,3253]},{"content":"There are two ways to run a job with recommended settings:","pos":[3255,3313]},{"content":"Run a Single Assessment with Recommended Settings","pos":[3320,3369]},{"content":"Use a Template with Recommended Settings","pos":[3394,3434]},{"pos":[3495,3544],"content":"Run a Single Assessment with Recommended Settings"},{"content":"Running an assessment with the recommended settings is quick and easy.","pos":[3546,3616]},{"content":"The settings are defined by Microsoft to make sure that the results can be compared across different computer configurations or over time on the same computer.","pos":[3617,3776]},{"content":"In this exercise, you run a single assessment using the predefined recommended settings.","pos":[3777,3865]},{"content":"Watch the video demonstration:","pos":[3867,3897]},{"content":"To run a single assessment with the recommended settings","pos":[4249,4305]},{"pos":[4313,4403],"content":"Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Start<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, type “assessment console”, and then click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Windows Assessment Console<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>."},{"content":"The Windows Assessment Console opens.","pos":[4409,4446]},{"content":"On the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Home<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page, click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Run Individual Assessments<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>.","pos":[4452,4511]},{"content":"In the details pane on the right, click the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Windows UI performance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> assessment, and then in the lower-right corner, click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Run<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>.","pos":[4512,4645]},{"pos":[4651,4707],"content":"If the User Account Control window opens, click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Yes<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>."},{"content":"Before the job starts, the job checks the computer configuration to make sure that the assessment can run successfully.","pos":[4713,4832]},{"content":"The job generates error messages, warnings, and informational messages based on the computer configuration and the requirements of the assessment.","pos":[4833,4979]},{"content":"The notifications appear in the Assessment Launcher dialog box as follows:","pos":[4980,5054]},{"content":"Errors block the start of the job.","pos":[5064,5098]},{"content":"Error messages appear when the job finds a problem with the computer hardware or configuration that must be fixed before the job can continue.","pos":[5099,5241]},{"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Start<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> button is not available in the dialog box if an error message appears.","pos":[5242,5326]},{"content":"After you fix blocking errors, you can click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Refresh<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> to check the computer again and continue the job.","pos":[5327,5433]},{"content":"Warnings appear when the job finds a problem that does not block running the job, but may affect the results.","pos":[5443,5552]},{"content":"You can review the warnings and take action, or ignore the warnings and click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Start<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.","pos":[5553,5641]},{"content":"Informational messages provide additional instructions or information about actions that will be taken when the job runs.","pos":[5651,5772]},{"content":"After you’ve read the information, click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Start<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> to begin the job.","pos":[5773,5841]},{"pos":[5847,6058],"content":"**Important**  \nDo not interact with the computer while the job is running. You will see activities while the job is running. When the job finishes, the results will appear in the Windows Assessment Console.","leadings":["","    "],"nodes":[{"content":"Important","pos":[2,11]},{"content":"Do not interact with the computer while the job is running. You will see activities while the job is running. When the job finishes, the results will appear in the Windows Assessment Console.","pos":[16,207],"nodes":[{"content":"Do not interact with the computer while the job is running.","pos":[0,59]},{"content":"You will see activities while the job is running.","pos":[60,109]},{"content":"When the job finishes, the results will appear in the Windows Assessment Console.","pos":[110,191]}]}]},{"content":"The results of this assessment show rendering and responsiveness metrics.","pos":[6067,6140]},{"content":"Search performance metrics include the time that is required for various aspects of Search to be completed and displayed.","pos":[6141,6262]},{"content":"Transition performance metrics include delays, frame rates, and glitches.","pos":[6263,6336]},{"content":"Responsiveness results are measured in milliseconds.","pos":[6337,6389]},{"content":"Low numbers mean that the computer is faster and more responsive.","pos":[6390,6455]},{"content":"For rendering, the results show the frame rate and the number of glitches that occur.","pos":[6456,6541]},{"content":"A good user experience has high frame rates and few glitches.","pos":[6542,6603]},{"content":"Issues and recommendations are based on these metrics.","pos":[6605,6659]},{"content":"Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Issues<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, and expand the information that appears in the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Details<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> pane on the right to understand the issue and the recommendations.","pos":[6660,6803]},{"content":"In most cases, you can also click the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>WPA in-depth analysis<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> link to further analyze an issue.","pos":[6804,6901]},{"pos":[6944,6984],"content":"Use a Template with Recommended Settings"},{"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Home<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> tab provides easy access to some predefined jobs