>**</ept>.","pos":[8520,8557]},{"content":"By default, this check box is cleared.","pos":[8558,8596]},{"content":"Select this check box to stop the job from completing if an error occurs.","pos":[8597,8670]},{"content":"This setting is useful when a job takes a long time to run.","pos":[8671,8730]},{"content":"If an error occurs and this check box is selected, this setting can prevent long wait times.","pos":[8731,8823]},{"content":"For shorter jobs, it is generally not necessary to stop the job if an error occurs.","pos":[8824,8907]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Keep all temporary files created by assessments<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.","pos":[8917,8969]},{"content":"By default, this check box is cleared.","pos":[8970,9008]},{"content":"Select this check box if you want to later review the files that the assessment created while the assessment was running.","pos":[9009,9130]},{"content":"Click the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Driver verification<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> assessment to see the assessment settings.","pos":[9136,9212]},{"content":"Make sure that <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Use recommended settings<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> is selected.","pos":[9213,9269]},{"content":"Assessment settings vary for each assessment.","pos":[9275,9320]},{"content":"For example, the other two assessments in this job, the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Driver certification prevalidation<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> assessment and the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>First boot performance<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> assessment don’t have configurable assessment settings.","pos":[9321,9517]},{"pos":[9523,9580],"content":"To run this job, click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Run<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> in the lower-right corner."},{"pos":[9586,9646],"content":"If the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>User Account Control<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> window opens, click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Yes<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>."},{"pos":[9652,9760],"content":"When the Microsoft Assessment Launcher window appears, click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Details<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> to monitor the progress of the job."},{"pos":[9766,10009],"content":"**Important**  \nIt is okay to monitor the job progress in the Assessment Launcher window, but do not interact with the computer in any other way while the job is running. You might also see a console window appear while the job is running.","leadings":["","    "],"nodes":[{"content":"Important","pos":[2,11]},{"content":"It is okay to monitor the job progress in the Assessment Launcher window, but do not interact with the computer in any other way while the job is running. You might also see a console window appear while the job is running.","pos":[16,239],"nodes":[{"content":"It is okay to monitor the job progress in the Assessment Launcher window, but do not interact with the computer in any other way while the job is running.","pos":[0,154]},{"content":"You might also see a console window appear while the job is running.","pos":[155,223]}]}]},{"content":"The assessments run in the order they are listed in the job.","pos":[10022,10082]},{"content":"First the Driver Verification assessment verifies that your computer contains the correct set of drivers.","pos":[10083,10188]},{"content":"Then the Driver Certification Prevalidation assessment verifies that installed drivers qualify for the Windows Certification Program.","pos":[10189,10322]},{"content":"The last assessment to run is the First Boot Performance assessment which examines the Event Trace Log (ETL) files created during Windows setup and OOBE to identify issues that affect the time that is required to boot Windows and display the Start screen the first time that the end user starts the computer.","pos":[10323,10631]},{"content":"When all three assessments are completed, the results open in the assessment console.","pos":[10632,10717]},{"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>View Results<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page contains a run information table, assessment results tables, a details pane on the right, and a metric char