">**</bpt>X<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> to remove the assessment.","pos":[14366,14481]},{"content":"Do the same for the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Minifilter diagnostic: Internet Explorer<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> assessment.","pos":[14482,14558]},{"pos":[14564,14672],"content":"Select the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Internet Explorer startup performance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> assessment to see the assessment settings on the right."},{"pos":[14678,14810],"content":"Under <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Settings<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, clear the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Use recommended settings<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> check box and select the <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Enable Minifilter Diagnostic Mode<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> check box."},{"content":"This setting identifies performance issues with minifilter drivers during Internet Explorer launch.","pos":[14816,14915]},{"pos":[14921,15030],"content":"Select the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Internet Explorer browsing performance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> assessment to see the assessment settings on the right."},{"pos":[15036,15187],"content":"Under <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Settings<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, clear the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Use recommended settings<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> check box and change the <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Internet Explorer View<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> to <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>Internet Explorer on the desktop<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept>."},{"content":"This setting enables you to assess the browsing performance of Internet Explorer when it is ran on the desktop instead of in the new Windows UI.","pos":[15193,15337]},{"pos":[15343,15383],"content":"Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Run<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> in the lower-right corner."},{"pos":[15389,15449],"content":"If the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>User Account Control<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> window opens, click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Yes<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>."},{"content":"Before the job starts, the job checks the computer configuration to make sure that the assessments can run successfully.","po